00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:50,570
Let's go.

290
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:52,240
No, don't pull so hard.

291
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:53,960
You go. You.

292
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:55,040
Xinxin, let go.

293
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,600
Let go, miss.

294
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:58,840
Stop struggling.

295
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:00,720
Why are you hitting me?

296
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,160
I'm sorry.

297
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:01,880
Let go of him.

298
00:15:01,880 --> 00:15:03,080
I'm so sorry.

299
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:05,280
I'm so sorry.

300
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:08,160
No, sis, please go take care of the child in the car first.

301
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:08,960
Don't worry.

302
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:09,820
Come, sit here.

303
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:28,130
The internal fixation looks good.

304
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:31,210
Do you know how lucky you are to have met me?

305
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:36,560
Here.

306
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:28,760
You said you would

307
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,210
wait for me forever.

308
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:32,260
I believed you.

309
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:35,640
So I got divorced.

310
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:37,600
And came back to find you.

311
00:16:37,880 --> 00:16:39,360
I've always known

312
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:41,570
that men's words can't be trusted.

313
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:44,920
If my mother hadn't been so eager to have a grandchild,

314
00:16:44,920 --> 00:16:46,850
I would never have gotten married.

315
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:49,680
And my mother threatened

316
00:16:50,920 --> 00:16:54,160
to leave her inheritance to her grandchild.

317
00:16:56,760 --> 00:16:59,820
It seems we were destined to meet but not to be together.

318
00:17:00,800 --> 00:17:01,600
Alright then.

319
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:04,599
We'll keep each other in our hearts.

320
00:17:05,280 --> 00:17:06,319
From now on,

321
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:09,200
I won't disturb your happy life anymore.

322
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:10,520
Weiwei.

323
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:13,119
You know what?

324
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:16,359
That place in my heart

325
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:18,280
has always been yours.

326
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:21,250
The reason I got married

327
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:23,819
was because I missed you too much.

328
00:17:24,079 --> 00:17:25,680
I wanted to find someone else

329
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:27,240
to take your place,

330
00:17:27,599 --> 00:17:29,600
to fill the void of missing you.

331
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:30,520
Really?

332
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:31,320
Really.

333
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,560
Take me to meet your wife.

334
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:37,160
What are you going to do?

335
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:37,960
Don't worry.

336
00:17:38,520 --> 00:17:40,240
I'm not going there to make trouble.

337
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:41,880
It's just that if you two

338
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:44,280
want to continue living happily together,

339
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:46,920
we need to resolve what happened that day.

340
00:17:47,760 --> 00:17:48,620
Remember this.

341
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:51,520
No matter what you've done to me,

342
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:52,960
I still love you.

343
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:55,360
As long as I see you happy,

344
00:17:55,600 --> 00:17:57,280
I'll do anything for you.

345
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:03,600
Thank you.

346
00:18:17,280 --> 00:18:19,010
Xinxin, you're finally awake.

347
00:18:20,080 --> 00:18:20,940
Where's my son?

348
00:18:21,040 --> 00:18:22,900
Don't worry. He's in the nursery.

349
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,960
You were completely drunk last night.

350
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:26,320
Someone from the pet hospital

351
00:18:26,320 --> 00:18:27,320
brought you home.

352
00:18:28,320 --> 00:18:30,250
What person from the pet hospital?

353
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:31,480
An older man.

354
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:33,240
Xinxin.

355
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:34,800
I don't mean to lecture you, but

356
00:18:34,800 --> 00:18:36,680
you're a mother now.

357
00:18:36,840 --> 00:18:39,360
You can't be as reckless as before.

358
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:40,400
I know.

359
00:18:41,360 --> 00:18:42,200
You...

360
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,160
Qin Gang is here.

361
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:45,900
You guys...

362
00:18:46,120 --> 00:18:47,520
How dare you show up here!

363
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:48,480
Get out!

364
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:50,280
Qin Gang explained everything to me.

365
00:18:50,280 --> 00:18:51,560
You misunderstood, Xinxin.

366
00:18:51,560 --> 00:18:52,040
What?

367
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:53,960
Listen to me.

368
00:18:53,960 --> 00:18:56,040
This is my client, Liu Wei.

369
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:57,360
The other day,

370
00:18:57,720 --> 00:18:59,160
she found out about our misunderstanding,

371
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:01,360
so she came specially to explain.

372
00:19:01,840 --> 00:19:03,160
You must be Wan Xinxin.

373
00:19:03,720 --> 00:19:05,480
So young and beautiful.

374
00:19:05,560 --> 00:19:07,160
Mr. Qin is so lucky.

375
00:19:07,880 --> 00:19:10,480
I'm Liu Wei, Mr. Qin's client.

376
00:19:11,120 --> 00:19:12,560
I heard that day,

377
00:19:12,560 --> 00:19:15,160
because of me, you two had a misunderstanding.

378
00:19:15,280 --> 00:19:16,410
Misunderstanding?

379
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:18,280
You were on the office couch

380
00:19:18,280 --> 00:19:19,840
hugging my husband.

381
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:22,320
I saw it with my own eyes and you call it a misunderstanding?

382
00:19:22,320 --> 00:19:24,240
Do you think I'm blind?

383
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:26,040
Don't be angry. Let me explain.

384
00:19:26,360 --> 00:19:27,640
It's all my fault.

385
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:29,000
That day I accidentally

386
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,640
spilled coffee on Mr. Qin.

387
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:32,080
When you arrived,

388
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:34,200
I was helping him clean his clothes.

389
00:19:34,320 --> 00:19:36,780
That's why the misunderstanding happened.

390
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:38,600
Honey,

391
00:19:39,280 --> 00:19:40,740
is what she's saying true?

392
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:41,640
Well...

393
00:19:43,080 --> 00:19:44,680
You don't have to believe me,

394
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:47,120
but you must trust your husband.

395
00:19:48,320 --> 00:19:49,850
This is a small gift from me.

396
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:51,480
Please accept it.

397
00:19:53,120 --> 00:19:55,360
I'll be going now. You take good rest.

398
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:58,520
Mr. Qin, take good care of your wife.

399
00:19:58,680 --> 00:19:59,800
I'll be going now.

400
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:00,820
Moon

401
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:05,720
Xinxin,

402
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:08,660
what mistress would come apologize to the wife?

403
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:10,160
Exactly. See?

404
00:20:10,320 --> 00:20:11,480
My client

405
00:20:11,520 --> 00:20:14,180
came specially to apologize and explain to you.

406
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:16,360
Besides, Qin Gang isn't stupid.

407
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:17,720
You two just got married,

408
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:19,080
and you've had a healthy baby boy.

409
00:20:19,080 --> 00:20:20,520
How could he bear to leave you?

410
00:20:20,520 --> 00:20:21,320
You have no idea,

411
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:24,200
he was so worried last night, looking everywhere for you.

412
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,360
I didn't sleep all night

413
00:20:25,360 --> 00:20:26,600
watching over you.

414
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:28,600
Right? Don't you agree?

415
00:20:36,560 --> 00:20:39,720
Honey, is what she's saying true?

416
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,000
Open the door!

417
00:20:59,440 --> 00:21:00,560
Open up now!

418
00:21:05,120 --> 00:21:06,040
Open the door!

419
00:21:06,800 --> 00:21:07,960
Sir, wait a moment.

420
00:21:11,280 --> 00:21:12,680
Sir, what can I do for you?

421
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:15,320
Sir?

422
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,080
Sir?

423
00:21:17,080 --> 00:21:18,160
Cut the nonsense.

424
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:21,080
Someone saw you pick up my son yesterday.

425
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:22,760
Where have you hidden him?

426
00:21:22,760 --> 00:21:24,720
No, I...

427
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:26,160
My son!

428
00:21:26,880 --> 00:21:28,000
What's wrong with you?

429
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:28,760
Is this your dog?

430
00:21:28,760 --> 00:21:29,760
Who did this to you?

431
00:21:29,760 --> 00:21:31,960
Sir, yesterday I caught it at the beach.

432
00:21:32,120 --> 00:21:34,200
How could you do this to it?

433
00:21:34,560 --> 00:21:35,400
No, it's me.

434
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,240
Listen to me.

435
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:37,120
How could you do this to it?

436
00:21:37,120 --> 00:21:38,320
I didn't harm it.

437
00:21:38,320 --> 00:21:39,520
Sir, sir, come here.

438
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:40,840
You've done this to it.

439
00:21:40,840 --> 00:21:41,480
Sir!

440
00:21:41,920 --> 00:21:43,160
If you have any issues, take it up with me.

441
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:43,600
No, no.

442
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:45,080
Ming, what's going on here?

443
00:21:45,080 --> 00:21:46,340
Are you the owner here?

444
00:21:46,520 --> 00:21:47,680
Yes, I'm the owner.

445
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:49,250
Someone from your place

446
00:21:49,360 --> 00:21:52,120
injured my son.

447
00:21:52,600 --> 00:21:55,320
You must give me an explanation today.

448
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:56,240
Look, sir,

449
00:21:56,320 --> 00:21:57,440
you don't have any proof.

450
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:59,080
You can't falsely accuse people, right?

451
00:21:59,080 --> 00:21:59,840
What proof?

452
00:22:00,040 --> 00:22:02,680
I saw it with my own eyes yesterday.

453
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:04,680
He was the one who hit him.

454
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:05,480
He was the one who did it.

455
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:06,540
Sir, how could I...

456
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:07,640
Sir, sir.

457
00:22:07,760 --> 00:22:08,960
Please calm down. Please calm down.

458
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:09,920
Listen to what our doctor has to say.

459
00:22:09,920 --> 00:22:10,720
Look, could you please calm down

460
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:11,680
and let me say something?

461
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:12,440
That's right.

462
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:14,160
I didn't hit it. I saved it.

463
00:22:14,160 --> 00:22:15,720
I've just finished operating on it.

464
00:22:15,720 --> 00:22:16,560
You came in here

465
00:22:16,560 --> 00:22:18,120
and didn't even give me a chance to speak.

466
00:22:18,120 --> 00:22:19,180
Listen carefully.

467
00:22:19,320 --> 00:22:22,160
Our doctor saved your dog.

468
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,860
You're talking nonsense.

469
00:22:24,080 --> 00:22:26,160
If you don't give me an explanation today,

470
00:22:26,160 --> 00:22:28,120
I'm not leaving.

471
00:22:28,120 --> 00:22:29,000
Look, sir,

472
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:31,640
if you really claim I hit your dog, show me the evidence.

473
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:32,280
Do you have evidence?

474
00:22:32,280 --> 00:22:33,480
You say you didn't hit it.

475
00:22:33,480 --> 00:22:34,280
Didn't hit it.

476
00:22:35,280 --> 00:22:36,760
Then what evidence do you have?

477
00:22:36,760 --> 00:22:38,490
Who can prove you didn't hit it?

478
00:22:40,040 --> 00:22:41,480
Who can prove it? Tell me.

479
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:44,100
Someone really did see it.

480
00:23:01,320 --> 00:23:02,880
It's normal. The child is completely fine.

481
00:23:02,880 --> 00:23:03,810
Good. Thank you.

482
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:07,000
Please come in.

483
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:09,240
Everything is normal.

484
00:23:10,880 --> 00:23:11,840
Now I can relax.

485
00:23:11,840 --> 00:23:12,320
Hello.

486
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:14,920
Hello. You are?

487
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:16,200
I'm

488
00:23:18,840 --> 00:23:20,920
The rideshare guy.

489
00:23:21,080 --> 00:23:23,010
Dr. Hua Ming from the pet hospital.

490
00:23:25,360 --> 00:23:26,760
I brought you some fruit.

491
00:23:27,760 --> 00:23:29,560
You even bought me fruit.

492
00:23:30,080 --> 00:23:32,400
No, I should have been the one visiting you.

493
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:34,920
And you bought me fruit. This is so embarrassing.

494
00:23:34,920 --> 00:23:38,080
Um, I drank too much yesterday.

495
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:41,440
I didn't cause you too much trouble, did I?

496
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:44,640
No, not at all.

497
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:45,920
You don't need to say anything. I know.

498
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:48,120
I have this one problem.

499
00:23:48,160 --> 00:23:49,880
When I drink too much, I always do

500
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:51,520
really strange things.

501
00:23:51,920 --> 00:23:53,400
I came to ask for your help.

502
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:55,280
You need my help?

503
00:23:57,800 --> 00:24:00,480
I'll help if I can.

504
00:24:00,560 --> 00:24:01,920
You can definitely help with this.

505
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:05,080
When you and the baby were in the car,

506
00:24:05,360 --> 00:24:06,480
I suddenly saw

507
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:08,440
a dog hit by a car on the roadside.

508
00:24:09,560 --> 00:24:11,320
I got out and rescued the dog.

509
00:24:11,320 --> 00:24:12,760
Now the dog's owner has found me

510
00:24:12,760 --> 00:24:14,200
and claims I hit the dog.

511
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:15,360
I want you to go

512
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:16,880
and be my witness

513
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:18,880
to testify that I didn't hit the dog.

514
00:24:19,080 --> 00:24:19,800
Right now?

515
00:24:19,800 --> 00:24:20,560
Yes, let's go now.

516
00:24:20,560 --> 00:24:21,560
No problem.

517
00:24:22,040 --> 00:24:23,040
Oh, wait. I can't.

518
00:24:23,560 --> 00:24:25,400
I'm staying at a postpartum care center.

519
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:27,520
I need someone to vouch for me to get permission to leave.

520
00:24:27,520 --> 00:24:29,040
Not a witness, a guarantor.

521
00:24:29,040 --> 00:24:32,440
Or you could go to the front desk and ask for leave on my behalf.

522
00:24:32,960 --> 00:24:34,480
Although we know each other,

523
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:35,640
your surname is Wan?

524
00:24:35,760 --> 00:24:36,720
Wan Xinxin.

525
00:24:36,720 --> 00:24:38,120
Okay, thank you.

526
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:39,040
Thank you.

527
00:24:39,040 --> 00:24:40,240
This baby is so cute.

528
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:41,640
You're buying fruit too?

529
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:44,680
Son.

530
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:46,280
Honey,

531
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:48,960
we can go out again. Did you know that?

532
00:24:56,360 --> 00:24:57,320
What's this for?

533
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:00,240
That's a dog language translator.

534
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:01,720
Dog language translator?

535
00:25:02,840 --> 00:25:03,840
That's so fancy!

536
00:25:10,600 --> 00:25:12,920
What's that hanging in the front of your car?

537
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,580
That's a photo of my daughter.

538
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:16,040
Can I see it?

539
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:20,120
Thank you.

540
00:25:22,560 --> 00:25:24,120
Such a loving man,

541
00:25:24,520 --> 00:25:26,250
hanging his daughter's photo.

542
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,600
Your daughter is so grown up.

543
00:25:29,280 --> 00:25:31,140
She doesn't look like you though.

544
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:33,400
Why isn't there a photo of your wife?

545
00:25:34,720 --> 00:25:36,380
You're not divorced, are you?

546
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:38,500
Thank you. Can I have it back, please?

547
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:39,960
Sure.

548
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:56,160
Stop the car! Pull over!

549
00:25:57,120 --> 00:25:57,840
Stop!

550
00:26:07,280 --> 00:26:07,760
Wait,

551
00:26:07,760 --> 00:26:09,420
Miss Wan, where are you going?

552
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:11,000
Wait for me here.

553
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:13,480
You can't park here.

554
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:15,240
Miss Wan!

555
00:26:36,360 --> 00:26:37,640
Are you looking for me?

556
00:26:47,040 --> 00:26:48,760
Were you just with my husband?

557
00:26:49,080 --> 00:26:50,010
Come in quickly.

558
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:11,320
I'm Qin Gang's client.

559
00:27:12,520 --> 00:27:14,360
But I'm also his ex-girlfriend.

560
00:27:14,720 --> 00:27:15,720
I love him.

561
00:27:16,240 --> 00:27:17,400
And he loves me too.

562
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:19,560
You two have only known each other

563
00:27:19,560 --> 00:27:20,890
for just one short year.

564
00:27:21,120 --> 00:27:22,440
But he and I

565
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:24,770
have known each other for almost 10 years.

566
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:27,600
You're nothing but a substitute.

567
00:27:28,720 --> 00:27:30,800
There's no real love between you two.

568
00:27:31,360 --> 00:27:32,360
That's nonsense!

569
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:34,960
We are married now.

570
00:27:35,760 --> 00:27:37,440
We've got our marriage certificate.

571
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:38,880
He is my husband now.

572
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:41,520
We already have a child together.

573
00:27:41,520 --> 00:27:43,360
Do you think having a child

574
00:27:43,360 --> 00:27:45,080
can keep a man's heart?

575
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:47,280
You're just the other woman now.

