00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:49,290
What do you have to compete with me?

577
00:27:51,120 --> 00:27:52,360
Listen to this.

578
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:55,000
That place in my heart

579
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:56,920
has always been yours.

580
00:27:58,120 --> 00:27:59,520
The reason I got married.

581
00:28:02,800 --> 00:28:04,800
is that I wanted to find someone else

582
00:28:04,800 --> 00:28:06,240
to replace you.

583
00:28:23,120 --> 00:28:24,680
You've been paid so much money.

584
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:26,080
What are you even good for?

585
00:28:26,080 --> 00:28:27,600
Handing a patient over

586
00:28:27,600 --> 00:28:29,360
to a complete stranger.

587
00:28:30,440 --> 00:28:32,000
Dr. Hua is not a stranger.

588
00:28:32,360 --> 00:28:33,890
He's my college classmate.

589
00:28:34,320 --> 00:28:36,840
Besides, Wan Xinxin said she knows him too.

590
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:39,400
And we got Mr. Qin's approval.

591
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,040
Director Li.

592
00:28:40,040 --> 00:28:41,680
It's okay. Please go ahead with your work.

593
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:43,720
Sorry for the trouble. I'll talk to her myself.

594
00:28:43,720 --> 00:28:44,600
Fine.

595
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:46,560
I still have questions. Why did you let her leave?

596
00:28:46,560 --> 00:28:47,800
I really don't know.

597
00:28:47,800 --> 00:28:48,880
You're a grown man.

598
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:50,840
How could you not keep an eye on a young girl?

599
00:28:50,840 --> 00:28:52,560
Listen, Wan Xinxin has already run away.

600
00:28:52,560 --> 00:28:53,520
So think about it.

601
00:28:53,520 --> 00:28:54,920
Is there anywhere she might have gone?

602
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:55,920
I'll get people to search for her.

603
00:28:55,920 --> 00:28:57,000
We need to find her.

604
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:57,840
How would I know?

605
00:28:57,840 --> 00:28:58,960
What's going on? Didn't you tell me

606
00:28:58,960 --> 00:28:59,520
Qin Gang,

607
00:28:59,520 --> 00:29:01,200
that she'd just give testimony and come back?

608
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:01,760
Yes, Mr. Qin.

609
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:03,080
I didn't expect she would run away.

610
00:29:03,080 --> 00:29:04,640
Did she run away or did you sell her?

611
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:05,240
Tell me.

612
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:05,760
I saved her.

613
00:29:05,760 --> 00:29:07,080
Where did you sell the mother and child?

614
00:29:07,080 --> 00:29:08,800
Tell me or I'm calling the police.

615
00:29:08,800 --> 00:29:09,800
Enough.

616
00:29:09,800 --> 00:29:10,800
That's enough.

617
00:29:11,480 --> 00:29:13,800
This isn't the first time she's run off.

618
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:15,200
She keeps doing this.

619
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:17,400
Forget it. I'm tired of this.

620
00:29:17,800 --> 00:29:19,960
Let's just leave it. I'm not looking for her anymore.

621
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:21,800
Qin Gang, don't be like this.

622
00:29:21,800 --> 00:29:23,760
Xinxin may be a bit willful,

623
00:29:23,760 --> 00:29:25,760
but you can't be so heartless.

624
00:29:25,760 --> 00:29:27,040
Just abandoning her like that.

625
00:29:27,040 --> 00:29:28,480
She's not alone anymore.

626
00:29:28,480 --> 00:29:30,320
Besides, you need to think about your son.

627
00:29:30,320 --> 00:29:30,840
Sister,

628
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:32,920
what am I supposed to think?

629
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:35,480
When you forced me to get married,

630
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:37,600
how did you promise me with your hand on your heart?

631
00:29:37,600 --> 00:29:40,060
You said Wan Xinxin had grown up and matured.

632
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:42,800
It's only been a few days since she gave birth,

633
00:29:42,800 --> 00:29:44,800
only a few days of behaving herself.

634
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:46,800
I married a wife,

635
00:29:46,800 --> 00:29:48,120
not a princess who needs constant pampering.

636
00:29:48,120 --> 00:29:50,640
If Wan Xinxin keeps causing trouble like this,

637
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:52,040
we're getting divorced.

638
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:56,960
It's okay, baby.

639
00:29:57,040 --> 00:29:58,080
Baby, it's alright.

640
00:29:58,080 --> 00:29:59,480
Let's be happy, okay?

641
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:05,960
Look, you've been crying

642
00:30:06,400 --> 00:30:09,600
for three hours. A full three hours now.

643
00:30:09,600 --> 00:30:11,400
Where do you get all these tears?

644
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:12,640
Can you please stop crying?

645
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:15,200
If you cry anymore, the Great Wall might collapse, you know?

646
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:16,860
You don't understand a thing!

647
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:19,960
My heart is broken now,

648
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:23,120
shattered into pieces.

649
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:26,360
I've always said that

650
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:28,480
the tears a woman sheds after marriage

651
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:31,560
are just the water that got into her head before marriage.

652
00:30:31,560 --> 00:30:32,560
I told you long ago

653
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:34,800
that Qin Gang was no good.

654
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:36,040
But you wouldn't listen.

655
00:30:36,040 --> 00:30:39,240
Now look what happened. You're facing the consequences.

656
00:30:41,200 --> 00:30:43,160
I'm already in such a state,

657
00:30:43,160 --> 00:30:45,920
don't you have any conscience?

658
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:48,440
Alright, alright.

659
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:49,480
Come on,

660
00:30:49,480 --> 00:30:50,920
get up, get up.

661
00:30:51,360 --> 00:30:53,480
Look at me. Look at me.

662
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:54,600
Why should I look at you?

663
00:30:54,600 --> 00:30:56,440
Come on, relax.

664
00:30:57,320 --> 00:30:58,560
Breathe.

665
00:30:59,560 --> 00:31:01,120
Inhale.

666
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:03,600
Relax again.

667
00:31:04,320 --> 00:31:05,760
Breathe again.

668
00:31:06,760 --> 00:31:07,960
How do you feel now?

669
00:31:11,360 --> 00:31:12,200
I'm hungry.

670
00:31:17,360 --> 00:31:18,200
Hey, Mom.

671
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:21,200
I asked you to send me photos of my grandson.

672
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:23,280
Why haven't you sent them yet?

673
00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:26,200
Don't worry.

674
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:27,720
Let me explain.

675
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:29,960
When Xiaobao was just born,

676
00:31:30,120 --> 00:31:31,920
I had a monk do some divination.

677
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:34,160
He said the baby was a bit premature,

678
00:31:34,640 --> 00:31:36,520
so we can't take photos too early.

679
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:39,080
Otherwise, it might capture his soul.

680
00:31:48,080 --> 00:31:49,880
Xu's Special Nutritional Meal.

681
00:31:49,920 --> 00:31:51,280
Premium ingredients.

682
00:31:51,840 --> 00:31:53,600
Specially customized for you.

683
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:55,760
Quick!

684
00:32:04,800 --> 00:32:06,240
What's wrong?

685
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:08,960
Why does this food taste bitter?

686
00:32:09,040 --> 00:32:09,720
Bitter?

687
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:10,560
Yes.

688
00:32:13,760 --> 00:32:14,920
I heard that

689
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:18,520
astragalus and codonopsis are good for new mothers,

690
00:32:18,520 --> 00:32:19,650
so I added a bit more.

691
00:32:20,360 --> 00:32:20,960
Too much.

692
00:32:22,840 --> 00:32:23,920
Alright, bye-bye.

693
00:32:29,520 --> 00:32:31,520
We can't even find the person and they still want photos.

694
00:32:31,520 --> 00:32:32,840
If she chose to run away,

695
00:32:32,840 --> 00:32:34,970
there's nothing you could do about it.

696
00:32:35,760 --> 00:32:37,960
Why not just tell the old lady the truth?

697
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:39,170
That won't work.

698
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:41,840
My mother's condition gets worse when she's anxious.

699
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:43,700
So what are you planning to do now?

700
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:45,920
What else? Get a divorce.

701
00:32:46,080 --> 00:32:47,120
It's not that simple.

702
00:32:47,120 --> 00:32:48,480
What about the child if you divorce?

703
00:32:48,480 --> 00:32:50,520
I'll raise the child myself, of course.

704
00:32:50,520 --> 00:32:52,560
When my little boy turns 18,

705
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:55,290
he'll kill that scoundrel and avenge his mother.

706
00:32:55,600 --> 00:32:57,080
Come on. First make sure

707
00:32:57,080 --> 00:32:58,940
you can survive the next 18 years.

708
00:32:58,960 --> 00:33:00,620
That's why I have you, don't I?

709
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:10,720
My lady, I have something to tell you.

710
00:33:11,320 --> 00:33:12,680
It's not good news, is it?

711
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:13,640
It is good news.

712
00:33:13,720 --> 00:33:14,280
Speak.

713
00:33:14,560 --> 00:33:16,020
I've taken a lucrative job

714
00:33:16,280 --> 00:33:17,540
and need to go on a trip.

715
00:33:17,560 --> 00:33:20,080
You just said you'd stick with me through thick and thin,

716
00:33:20,080 --> 00:33:22,720
and now this. Men are as reliable as pigs flying.

717
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:24,080
Look, while you were drowning in your emotional drama,

718
00:33:24,080 --> 00:33:25,440
I was signing a contract.

719
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,520
What's more important, the contract or me?

720
00:33:26,520 --> 00:33:27,160
You are.

721
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:27,600
Exactly.

722
00:33:27,600 --> 00:33:28,000
But...

723
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:28,840
But what?

724
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:34,080
You left with nothing,

725
00:33:34,280 --> 00:33:36,320
and I'm completely broke.

726
00:33:37,280 --> 00:33:39,210
I've arranged everything for you.

727
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:40,930
Don't worry.

728
00:33:47,440 --> 00:33:48,480
Wait, Xu Ke.

729
00:33:50,040 --> 00:33:50,960
Is this all the money you have?

730
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:52,960
And you're showing off your wallet?

731
00:33:53,120 --> 00:33:56,400
This is all I have, my dear.

732
00:33:56,840 --> 00:33:59,170
Don't worry, it'll last until I come back.

733
00:33:59,200 --> 00:34:01,120
Also, the gas bill

734
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:02,240
probably needs to be paid soon.

735
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:04,240
You'll need to pay it at the property management office.

736
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:05,840
So I have to deal with the gas bill too?

737
00:34:05,840 --> 00:34:07,840
Alright, I've told you everything.

738
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:09,480
When I return rich,

739
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:13,000
I'll treat you and your son to a life of luxury.

740
00:34:14,639 --> 00:34:15,880
Okay, let's try another one.

741
00:34:15,880 --> 00:34:16,880
Good, beautiful.

742
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:18,360
Come on, that's so sexy. Good.

743
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:19,280
Alright, let's go.

744
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:21,280
One, two. Show me your leg.

745
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:21,840
Good.

746
00:34:22,120 --> 00:34:23,360
Change the pose, change the pose.

747
00:34:23,360 --> 00:34:24,360
The eyes! Focus on the eyes!

748
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:25,400
Again, keep going.

749
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:25,760
Beautiful.

750
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:26,880
Come on, next one, next one.

751
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:27,639
Two.

752
00:34:33,719 --> 00:34:35,239
This one is so cute.

753
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:37,440
Look, honey. Isn't it pretty?

754
00:34:38,639 --> 00:34:39,900
You like it too, right?

755
00:34:44,159 --> 00:34:45,420
Why is it so expensive?

756
00:34:50,159 --> 00:34:51,480
Is this a parent-child matching outfit?

757
00:34:51,480 --> 00:34:52,080
Yes, it is.

758
00:34:52,600 --> 00:34:53,679
So cute.

759
00:34:53,719 --> 00:34:56,320
But this one isn't really suitable for your baby.

760
00:34:56,320 --> 00:34:57,880
How about this one?

761
00:34:59,120 --> 00:35:01,760
This one is nice too. It's suitable for him to wear now.

762
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:03,040
Okay, I'll take all of these.

763
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:03,480
Great!

764
00:35:04,200 --> 00:35:05,460
How much is it in total?

765
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,880
Hello, the total is 3,288.

766
00:35:09,640 --> 00:35:10,440
How much?

767
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:11,560
3,288.

768
00:35:22,920 --> 00:35:25,720
Anyway, you're joint property between me and him.

769
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:27,400
Go ahead and charge it.

770
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:28,040
Okay.

771
00:35:31,480 --> 00:35:33,540
So Wan Xinxin is shopping at the mall.

772
00:35:34,240 --> 00:35:35,200
I'll go find her.

773
00:35:35,880 --> 00:35:37,400
What's the point of going now?

774
00:35:37,400 --> 00:35:39,660
By the time you get there, she'll be gone.

775
00:35:43,200 --> 00:35:46,040
You got this credit card for Wan Xinxin, right?

776
00:35:47,240 --> 00:35:48,080
Yes.

777
00:35:48,080 --> 00:35:49,960
I used to manage all her money.

778
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:53,560
Actually, since you helped her get the card,

779
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:55,680
we could just cancel it.

780
00:35:55,680 --> 00:35:58,520
When she runs out of money, she'll naturally come back to you.

781
00:35:58,520 --> 00:35:59,320
That's right.

782
00:36:10,600 --> 00:36:12,960
Sweetie.

783
00:36:16,240 --> 00:36:18,840
Ruirui, it must be early morning where you are.

784
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:20,450
Why aren't you sleeping in?

785
00:36:20,600 --> 00:36:21,600
I miss you.

786
00:36:22,480 --> 00:36:25,560
Dad, it's the weekend. How could you forget?

787
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:30,560
Listen, Daddy is outside right now.

788
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,880
Can we video chat after I get home?

789
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:34,320
No. Go eat first.

790
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:35,250
Don't look at me.

791
00:36:35,880 --> 00:36:36,880
Yes, sir.

792
00:36:37,720 --> 00:36:38,440
Hurry up.

793
00:36:39,240 --> 00:36:40,200
Don't lie to me.

794
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:42,000
Okay, okay. Hey, Ruirui.

795
00:36:42,480 --> 00:36:44,560
I'll eat whatever you want me to eat.

796
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:47,890
Shopping malls are truly evil places.

797
00:36:48,280 --> 00:36:50,400
But Mom's feeling much better now.

798
00:36:52,920 --> 00:36:55,360
I suddenly have a craving for hot pot.

799
00:36:56,200 --> 00:36:59,480
No, I can't give in. I should go home and eat instant noodles.

800
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:00,680
But if I don't treat myself to something nice,

801
00:37:00,680 --> 00:37:02,320
how can I face my own stomach?

802
00:37:03,240 --> 00:37:04,480
Right, if I don't eat well,

803
00:37:04,480 --> 00:37:06,080
I won't have the strength to carry all this stuff home,

804
00:37:06,080 --> 00:37:06,560
right?

805
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:10,560
If I don't eat enough, I won't have energy to raise you either.

806
00:37:10,560 --> 00:37:11,680
Okay, it's decided then.

807
00:37:11,680 --> 00:37:12,410
Hot pot it is!

808
00:37:17,520 --> 00:37:18,240
Hello.

809
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:20,960
Can I leave my things here for now?

810
00:37:21,600 --> 00:37:22,200
Thank you.

811
00:37:28,760 --> 00:37:29,480
Thanks.

812
00:37:33,080 --> 00:37:33,800
Excuse me.

813
00:37:36,120 --> 00:37:37,280
Could you bring me some hot water?

814
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:38,840
I need to sterilize a baby bottle.

815
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:39,840
Great, thank you.

816
00:37:44,160 --> 00:37:46,200
Baby, daddy ordered double portions.

817
00:37:46,200 --> 00:37:48,000
I'll eat your favorite dishes for you.

818
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:49,480
We'll have food soon.

819
00:38:04,040 --> 00:38:06,500
Mom will feed you after she finishes eating.

820
00:38:23,680 --> 00:38:24,410
Oh, it's you.

821
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:26,520
It's not me.

822
00:38:26,520 --> 00:38:28,650
What do you mean it's not you? It is you.

823
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:30,080
Goodbye.

824
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:32,120
I should take you back to the maternity center.

825
00:38:32,120 --> 00:38:34,640
I was planning to go back.

826
00:38:35,240 --> 00:38:37,170
I'll go back after I finish eating.

827
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:38,240
Well...

828
00:38:38,640 --> 00:38:40,280
I ordered enough for two people.

829
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:41,280
Too much for just me.

830
00:38:41,280 --> 00:38:42,410
Let's eat together.

831
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:45,880
Don't be so polite.

832
00:38:45,880 --> 00:38:47,480
It's fine. Don't mention it.

833
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:54,940
Please.

834
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:56,360
Okay.

835
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:04,520
Waiter,

836
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:05,840
bring us a spicy pot.

837
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:06,440
Waiter,

838
00:39:07,120 --> 00:39:08,520
that won't be necessary.

839
00:39:09,200 --> 00:39:09,920
Well,

840
00:39:10,520 --> 00:39:11,560
during breastfeeding,

841
00:39:11,560 --> 00:39:13,320
it's not good to eat spicy food.

842
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:14,400
Actually,

843
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:18,530
I ordered a clear broth pot that hasn't been touched yet.

844
00:39:19,040 --> 00:39:20,120
Just have a bite.

845
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:28,320
Look at me, my brain isn't working properly.

846
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:29,760
Pregnancy makes you stupid for three years.

847
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:31,160
I haven't fed my baby yet.

848
00:39:31,760 --> 00:39:33,820
Maybe I should go feed the baby first.

849
00:39:34,240 --> 00:39:37,520
Feed the baby back at the maternity center. It won't take long.

850
00:39:37,520 --> 00:39:38,980
Let me feed the baby first.

851
00:39:41,640 --> 00:39:45,570
Here's the hot water you asked for. Do you want to sterilize the bottle?

852
00:39:46,120 --> 00:39:46,840
Thank you.

853
00:39:53,600 --> 00:39:54,920
Hurry up and eat something.

854
00:39:54,920 --> 00:39:58,650
After we finish eating, I'll take you back to the maternity center.

855
00:39:59,680 --> 00:40:01,280
Are you serious?

856
00:40:02,160 --> 00:40:04,560
I'm a grown woman. Can't I go back by myself?

857
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:07,760
No, miss, it's like this.

858
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:08,680
I rescued you.

859
00:40:09,360 --> 00:40:10,600
Let's not talk about this anymore.

860
00:40:10,600 --> 00:40:12,800
I'm the one who brought you out from the maternity center.

861
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:14,040
I promised them I'd take you back.

862
00:40:14,040 --> 00:40:15,240
After you return to the maternity center,

863
00:40:15,240 --> 00:40:17,240
whatever you do is none of my business.

864
00:40:17,240 --> 00:40:19,170
Hurry up and eat. We'll leave soon.

865
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:20,680
Listen, sir,

866
00:40:21,560 --> 00:40:23,220
why are you being so stubborn?

867
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:25,720
Yes, you saved me,

868
00:40:25,720 --> 00:40:27,580
but you can't control me forever.

869
00:40:27,760 --> 00:40:28,400
I'll say it again.

870
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:29,360
After I take you back,

871
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:31,890
whatever you want to do is none of my business.

872
00:40:35,600 --> 00:40:36,530
Hurry up and eat.

873
00:40:41,600 --> 00:40:43,240
Oh! Oh no!

874
00:40:43,600 --> 00:40:45,920
I need to use the restroom.

875
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:52,370
Go ahead, child. I'll keep an eye on it for you.

876
00:40:52,800 --> 00:40:55,000
Okay. Make sure you watch it carefully.

877
00:40:55,040 --> 00:40:55,640
I will.

878
00:41:04,080 --> 00:41:06,000
Baby, your mom is

879
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:09,200
very sneaky.

880
00:41:12,600 --> 00:41:13,160
Ma'am,

881
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:15,000
are you from the neighborhood committee downstairs?

882
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:15,720
Yes, I am.

883
00:41:16,480 --> 00:41:17,840
I have a favor to ask you.

884
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:18,440
What is it?

885
00:41:30,240 --> 00:41:30,770
Don't go.

886
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:32,580
What's wrong with you?

887
00:41:37,120 --> 00:41:38,980
Do you think this is appropriate?

888
00:42:16,160 --> 00:42:17,040
Huahua, are you asking for trouble?

889
00:42:17,040 --> 00:42:19,240
It took you forever to answer the phone.

890
00:42:19,520 --> 00:42:20,850
Don't think I don't know

891
00:42:21,360 --> 00:42:22,720
where you took your phone.

892
00:42:22,720 --> 00:42:24,650
Put the phone against your ear now.

893
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:27,560
I'm listening, I'm listening.

894
00:42:27,560 --> 00:42:28,480
Your Highness,

895
00:42:29,160 --> 00:42:31,040
do you have any instructions?

896
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:33,530
I'm in a hurry, please get to the point.

897
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:35,640
What urgent matter? You're just chasing girls,

898
00:42:35,640 --> 00:42:37,040
don't think I don't know.

899
00:43:44,560 --> 00:43:45,160
Yang Ming.

900
00:43:46,320 --> 00:43:46,720
Wang Yaping.

